---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="H2OPE – Lepší spánek, rychlejší regenerace, více energie" hasHero={true}>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero-wave-bg-D3SlsVy3.png" alt="" class="hero-wave" />
    </div>
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">AI-Powered Wellness</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span class="cs-only">Lepší spánek<br />Rychlejší regenerace<br />Více energie</span>
        <span class="en-only">Better Sleep<br />Faster Recovery<br />More Energy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub"><span class="cs-only">Napsáno životem, podpořeno srdcem.</span><span class="en-only">Written by life, backed by heart.</span></p>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">500+</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label"><span class="cs-only">klientů</span><span class="en-only">clients</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">6 000</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label"><span class="cs-only">odinhalovaných hodin</span><span class="en-only">inhaled hours</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">3 <span class="cs-only">roky</span><span class="en-only">yrs</span></span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label"><span class="cs-only">praxe</span><span class="en-only">of practice</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="/pro-firmy" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Pro firmy →</span><span class="en-only">For Companies →</span></a>
        <a href="/pro-jednotlivce" class="btn btn-outline"><span class="cs-only">Pro jednotlivce</span><span class="en-only">For Individuals</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CO JE MOLEKULÁRNÍ VODÍK -->
  <section class="molecule-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="mol-label"><span class="cs-only">O vodíkové terapii</span><span class="en-only">About Hydrogen Therapy</span></p>
      <p class="mol-sub"><span class="cs-only">Jednoduše vysvětleno, bez zbytečného žargonu</span><span class="en-only">Simply explained, without unnecessary jargon</span></p>
      <div class="molecule-grid">
        <div class="molecule-cards">
          <div class="molecule-card">
            <div class="molecule-card-icon">H₂</div>
            <div>
              <h3><span class="cs-only">Co to je</span><span class="en-only">What It Is</span></h3>
              <p><span class="cs-only">Molekulární vodík (H₂) je nejmenší molekula ve vesmíru. Díky své velikosti se může dostat prakticky kamkoli v těle – tam, kam větší molekuly nemají přístup.</span><span class="en-only">Molecular hydrogen (H₂) is the smallest molecule in the universe. Due to its size, it can reach practically anywhere in the body – places where larger molecules can't access.</span></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="molecule-card">
            <div class="molecule-card-icon">✦</div>
            <div>
              <h3><span class="cs-only">Proč se používá</span><span class="en-only">Why It's Used</span></h3>
              <p><span class="cs-only">Lidé vodík využívají pro podporu regenerace, energie a celkové pohody. Není to lék, ale podpůrný wellness nástroj pro ty, kdo chtějí o sebe pečovat aktivněji.</span><span class="en-only">People use hydrogen to support recovery, energy, and overall wellbeing. It's not a medicine, but a supportive wellness tool for those who want a more active approach to their health.</span></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="molecule-card">
            <div class="molecule-card-icon">→</div>
            <div>
              <h3><span class="cs-only">Jak terapie probíhá</span><span class="en-only">How Therapy Works</span></h3>
              <p><span class="cs-only">Konzultace → personalizovaný plán → pravidelné inhalace → průběžné sledování a úpravy programu dle Vašich potřeb.</span><span class="en-only">Consultation → personalized plan → regular inhalations → ongoing monitoring and adjustments based on your needs.</span></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="/jak-to-funguje" class="btn btn-outline-orange"><span class="cs-only">Chci vědět více</span><span class="en-only">Learn More</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="molecule-img">
          <img src="/images/h2ope-product-side-CxX-ZJVh.png" alt="H2OPE produkt" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VIDEO -->
  <section class="video-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="video-wrap">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AHFvYkVjhus"
          title="H2OPE Hydrogen Therapy"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROČ NA KANCLU -->
  <section class="office-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="office-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Pro firmy</span><span class="en-only">For Companies</span></p>
          <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Proč mít vodík na kanclu?</span><span class="en-only">Why Have Hydrogen at the Office?</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Protože je to skvělý benefit pro zaměstnance, ale pozor ještě lepší pro zaměstnavatele 🙂</span><span class="en-only">Because it's a great benefit for employees, but watch out – it's even better for employers 🙂</span></p>
          <ul class="office-list">
            <li>
              <span class="office-check">✓</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">Zaměstnanci mají lepší koncentraci a efektivitu</span><span class="en-only">Employees have better concentration and efficiency</span></span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="office-check">✓</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">Sníží se nemocnost ve firmě</span><span class="en-only">Reduced illness in the company</span></span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="office-check">✓</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">Lidé mají více energie</span><span class="en-only">People have more energy</span></span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pro-firmy" class="btn btn-orange" style="margin-top:2rem;display:inline-flex"><span class="cs-only">Chci nezávaznou konzultaci a zjistit více</span><span class="en-only">I want a free consultation and more info</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="office-visual">
          <img src="/images/audience-corporate-Dn4o_vV9.jpg" alt="Firemní wellness" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JAK FUNGUJE - 6 KROKŮ -->
  <section class="steps-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Proces</span><span class="en-only">Process</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Jak funguje vodíková terapie u H2OPE</span><span class="en-only">How Hydrogen Therapy Works at H2OPE</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">6 jednoduchých kroků k lepšímu zdraví</span><span class="en-only">6 simple steps to better health</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Workshop a nastavení</span><span class="en-only">Workshop & Setup</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Přijedeme za vámi, vše vám ukážeme a společně nastavíme.</span><span class="en-only">We'll come to you, show you everything, and set it up together.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Rychlý dotazník</span><span class="en-only">Quick Questionnaire</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Pár otázek pro správné doporučení na míru.</span><span class="en-only">A few questions for the right personalized recommendation.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Vyhodnocení</span><span class="en-only">Assessment</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">H2OPE Score a klíčové oblasti zaměření.</span><span class="en-only">H2OPE Score and key areas of focus.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">04</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Individuální plán</span><span class="en-only">Individual Plan</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Plán pro každého zaměstnance (volitelně testy pro větší přesnost).</span><span class="en-only">A plan for each employee (optional tests for greater accuracy).</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">05</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Inhalace v kanceláři</span><span class="en-only">Office Inhalation</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Jednoduchá sezení podle plánu.</span><span class="en-only">Simple sessions according to plan.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">06</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Průběžná péče</span><span class="en-only">Ongoing Care</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Úpravy podle dat a zpětné vazby.</span><span class="en-only">Adjustments based on data and feedback.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top:3rem">
        <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Chci nezávaznou konzultaci</span><span class="en-only">I want a free consultation</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRO KOHO - SLIDER -->
  <section class="audience-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Cílové skupiny</span><span class="en-only">Target Groups</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Pro koho je vodíková terapie</span><span class="en-only">Who Is Hydrogen Therapy For</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Každý má jiné cíle. Vyberte oblast, která je vám nejbližší.</span><span class="en-only">Everyone has different goals. Select the area closest to you.</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="audience-slider-wrap">
      <div class="audience-slider" id="audienceSlider">
        <div class="audience-card">
          <img src="/images/audience-corporate-Dn4o_vV9.jpg" alt="Korporátní klienti" />
          <div class="audience-card-body">
            <div class="audience-tag"><span class="cs-only">H₂EKTICKÁ PRÁCE?</span><span class="en-only">H₂ECTIC WORK?</span></div>
            <h3><span class="cs-only">Korporátní klienti</span><span class="en-only">Corporate Clients</span></h3>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Wellness benefit pro zaměstnance. Podpora regenerace a energie během náročného pracovního období. Možnost on-site terapeutických dnů.</span><span class="en-only">Wellness benefit for employees. Supporting recovery and energy during demanding work periods. Option for on-site therapy days.</span></p>
            <a href="/pro-firmy" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Řešení pro firmy →</span><span class="en-only">Business Solutions →</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-card">
          <img src="/images/audience-oncology-CSZjQL9Q.jpg" alt="Onkologičtí pacienti" />
          <div class="audience-card-body">
            <h3><span class="cs-only">Onkologičtí pacienti</span><span class="en-only">Oncology Patients</span></h3>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Podpůrná péče zaměřená na komfort, regeneraci a rovnováhu. Citlivý přístup pro období zvýšené zátěže.</span><span class="en-only">Supportive care focused on comfort, recovery, and balance. A sensitive approach for periods of increased stress.</span></p>
            <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Individuální konzultace →</span><span class="en-only">Individual Consultation →</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-card">
          <img src="/images/audience-autoimmune-D8k6ORg3.jpg" alt="Autoimunitní onemocnění" />
          <div class="audience-card-body">
            <h3><span class="cs-only">Autoimunitní onemocnění</span><span class="en-only">Autoimmune Conditions</span></h3>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Podpora celkové rovnováhy a regenerace při dlouhodobých zdravotních výzvách. Jemný a zodpovědný přístup.</span><span class="en-only">Supporting overall balance and recovery in long-term health challenges. A gentle and responsible approach.</span></p>
            <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Zjistit možnosti →</span><span class="en-only">Explore Options →</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-card">
          <img src="/images/audience-family-DSpp3RU4.jpg" alt="Děti a rodina" />
          <div class="audience-card-body">
            <h3><span class="cs-only">Děti a rodina</span><span class="en-only">Children & Family</span></h3>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Jemný přístup pro celou rodinu. Děti pouze v doprovodu rodičů. Bezpečnost a zodpovědnost na prvním místě.</span><span class="en-only">A gentle approach for the whole family. Children only with parental supervision. Safety and responsibility come first.</span></p>
            <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Konzultace pro rodiče →</span><span class="en-only">Parent Consultation →</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-card">
          <img src="/images/audience-sports-DLvN4tBA.jpg" alt="Sportovci" />
          <div class="audience-card-body">
            <h3><span class="cs-only">Sportovci</span><span class="en-only">Athletes</span></h3>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Podpora regenerace, výkonnosti a tréninkové rovnováhy. Rychlejší zotavení před i po zátěži.</span><span class="en-only">Supporting recovery, performance, and training balance. Faster recovery before and after exertion.</span></p>
            <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Pro sportovce →</span><span class="en-only">For Athletes →</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="slider-nav">
        <button class="slider-btn" id="slidePrev" aria-label="Předchozí">←</button>
        <button class="slider-btn" id="slideNext" aria-label="Další">→</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROČ H2OPE -->
  <section class="why-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Naše výhody</span><span class="en-only">Our Advantages</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Proč H2OPE</span><span class="en-only">Why H2OPE</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Co nás odlišuje od ostatních</span><span class="en-only">What sets us apart</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">👤</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Individuální přístup</span><span class="en-only">Individual Approach</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Každý plán je přizpůsobený vašim cílům, zdravotnímu stavu a životnímu stylu.</span><span class="en-only">Each plan is tailored to your goals, health status, and lifestyle.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">📊</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Strukturovaný proces</span><span class="en-only">Structured Process</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Od prvního dotazníku po průběžné úpravy – vše je jasné, měřitelné a transparentní.</span><span class="en-only">From the first questionnaire to ongoing adjustments – everything is clear, measurable, and transparent.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">🤖</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">FlowGen výhoda</span><span class="en-only">FlowGen Advantage</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Aplikace FlowGen vás provází celým procesem s AI doporučeními a sledováním pokroku.</span><span class="en-only">The FlowGen app guides you through the entire process with AI recommendations and progress tracking.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Zodpovědnost a vážnost</span><span class="en-only">Responsibility & Seriousness</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Nejsme alternativní medicína. Jsme wellness program s vážným přístupem k vašemu zdraví.</span><span class="en-only">We're not alternative medicine. We're a wellness program with a serious approach to your health.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">💬</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Transparentní komunikace</span><span class="en-only">Transparent Communication</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Žádné tajemství, žádné zázračné sliby. Jasné informace o tom, co můžete očekávat.</span><span class="en-only">No secrets, no miraculous promises. Clear information about what to expect.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">⚙️</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Profesionální vybavení</span><span class="en-only">Professional Equipment</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Používáme špičkové přístroje pro vodíkovou terapii.</span><span class="en-only">We use state-of-the-art equipment for hydrogen therapy.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ZKUŠENOSTI KLIENTŮ -->
  <section class="testimonials-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Reference</span><span class="en-only">Reviews</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Zkušenosti klientů</span><span class="en-only">Client Experiences</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Co říkají ti, kteří už vodíkovou terapii vyzkoušeli</span><span class="en-only">What those who've tried hydrogen therapy say</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote><span class="cs-only">„Po několika týdnech jsem si všiml, že se cítím odpočatější a mám více energie během dne."</span><span class="en-only">"After a few weeks I noticed I feel more rested and have more energy throughout the day."</span></blockquote>
          <cite><span class="cs-only">— Klient, 45 let</span><span class="en-only">— Client, 45 years old</span></cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote><span class="cs-only">„Oceňuji strukturovaný přístup a aplikaci, která mi pomáhá udržet pravidelnost."</span><span class="en-only">"I appreciate the structured approach and the app that helps me stay consistent."</span></blockquote>
          <cite><span class="cs-only">— Klientka, 38 let</span><span class="en-only">— Client, 38 years old</span></cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote><span class="cs-only">„Jako sportovec hledám cesty k rychlejší regeneraci. H2OPE mi v tom pomáhá."</span><span class="en-only">"As an athlete I'm always looking for ways to recover faster. H2OPE helps me with that."</span></blockquote>
          <cite><span class="cs-only">— Profesionální sportovec</span><span class="en-only">— Professional Athlete</span></cite>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="testimonials-note"><span class="cs-only">Toto jsou anonymizované zkušenosti klientů. Výsledky se mohou lišit.</span><span class="en-only">These are anonymized client experiences. Results may vary.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FLOWGEN -->
  <section class="flowgen-section" id="flowgen">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="flowgen-grid">
        <div class="flowgen-text">
          <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Technologie</span><span class="en-only">Technology</span></p>
          <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Aplikace FlowGen</span><span class="en-only">FlowGen App</span></h2>
          <p class="flowgen-tagline"><span class="cs-only">Vaše vodíková terapie pod kontrolou</span><span class="en-only">Your hydrogen therapy under control</span></p>
          <p class="flowgen-desc"><span class="cs-only">FlowGen je aplikace, která vás provází celým procesem vodíkové terapie. Sleduje vaše sezení, analyzuje pokrok a poskytuje personalizovaná AI doporučení.</span><span class="en-only">FlowGen is an app that guides you through the entire hydrogen therapy process. It tracks your sessions, analyzes progress, and provides personalized AI recommendations.</span></p>
          <div class="flowgen-features">
            <div class="flowgen-feature">
              <span class="ff-icon">📱</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">Mobilní aplikace</span><span class="en-only">Mobile App</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="flowgen-feature">
              <span class="ff-icon">📡</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">Sledování v reálném čase</span><span class="en-only">Real-time Tracking</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="flowgen-feature">
              <span class="ff-icon">🤖</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">AI doporučení</span><span class="en-only">AI Recommendations</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/pro-jednotlivce" class="btn btn-orange" style="margin-top:2rem;display:inline-flex"><span class="cs-only">Více o FlowGen</span><span class="en-only">Learn More About FlowGen</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="flowgen-visual">
          <img src="/images/h2ope-product-top-D4T-DMW8.png" alt="H2OPE přístroj" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><span class="cs-only">Nejste si jistí jak vám vodík pomůže?</span><span class="en-only">Not sure how hydrogen can help you?</span></h2>
